         <region style="defaultSpeaker" xml:id="speaker"></region>
      </layout>
   </head>
   <body xml:id="thebody" style="defaultCaption">
      <div xml:lang="en">
         <p begin="00:00:02.03" end="00:00:04.76" region="speaker">GSA allows vendors to increase their schedule</p>
         <p begin="00:00:04.76" end="00:00:07.06" region="speaker">prices in accordance with economic price</p>
         <p begin="00:00:07.06" end="00:00:08.16" region="speaker">adjustments.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:08.16" end="00:00:10.73" region="speaker">The pricing index to be used - whether it is the</p>
         <p begin="00:00:10.73" end="00:00:14.53" region="speaker">CPI, inflation, or another agreed-upon index - is</p>
         <p begin="00:00:14.53" end="00:00:17.86" region="speaker">typically determined prior to contract award.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:17.86" end="00:00:20.53" region="speaker">As this modification could potentially impact your</p>
         <p begin="00:00:20.53" end="00:00:22.73" region="speaker">projections of how much business you plan to do</p>
         <p begin="00:00:22.73" end="00:00:25.13" region="speaker">with the government, you may need to review and</p>
         <p begin="00:00:25.13" end="00:00:28.46" region="speaker">update your Commercial Sales Practice If so,</p>
         <p begin="00:00:28.46" end="00:00:31.26" region="speaker">click Yes and Save, upon which you will be taken</p>
         <p begin="00:00:31.26" end="00:00:33.40" region="speaker">through the CSP utility.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:33.40" end="00:00:36.03" region="speaker">Updating your CSP is covered in a different</p>
         <p begin="00:00:36.03" end="00:00:37.30" region="speaker">video.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:37.30" end="00:00:40.76" region="speaker">If this is not the case, select No and continue</p>
         <p begin="00:00:40.76" end="00:00:43.66" region="speaker">with the modification Enter the percentage</p>
         <p begin="00:00:43.66" end="00:00:45.33" region="speaker">increase you are requesting.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:45.33" end="00:00:46.93" region="speaker">Note that this should be pursuant to the</p>
         <p begin="00:00:46.93" end="00:00:50.13" region="speaker">agreed-upon terms of your schedule contract.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:50.13" end="00:00:52.73" region="speaker">In the textbox, provide the CO with enough</p>
         <p begin="00:00:52.73" end="00:00:56.66" region="speaker">information justifying your price increase.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:56.66" end="00:00:58.76" region="speaker">When you are finished click the &quot;Save and</p>
         <p begin="00:00:58.76" end="00:00:60.80" region="speaker">Continue&quot; button</p>
    </div>
